'''''Nike Air Max'''''是[[美國|美國]]體育用品公司[[Nike|Nike]]在1987年開始生產銷售的系列鞋類。Nike Air Max最早的設計者是Tinker Hatfield，他也是眾多[[Air_Jordan|Air Jordan]]系列鞋類的設計者<ref>{{cite news|last=Reidy|first=Tess|title=Nike's iconic Air Max trainer celebrates 25th anniversary with Tinker Hatfield|url=http://www.theguardian.com/fashion/2013/dec/14/nike-air-max-trainer-25-anniversary-tinker-hatfield|accessdate=23 December 2013|newspaper=The Guardian (UK)|date=14 December 2013|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230436/http://www.theguardian.com/fashion/2013/dec/14/nike-air-max-trainer-25-anniversary-tinker-hatfield|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Nike Air Max使用了空氣減震技術，並利用了透明設計來強調他的吸震能力。在很多時候，Nike Air Max已經成為一個流行文化標誌<ref>{{cite news|last=Lev|first=Michael A.|title=`Air Max Hunting' Shocks Japan -- Holdups, Beatings Blamed On Mania For Used Sneakers|newspaper=The Seattle Times|date=November 17, 1996|access-date=July 4, 2015|url=http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=19961117&slug=2360191|archive-date=2015-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704192457/http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=19961117&slug=2360191|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
